aim_ag_trenches
Created By Naticus 3/24/2010
http://www.jgcclan.net/

40 player max

Intro:
=======
This is an aim map designed with two trench areas on each side of the map with plenty of grenades handy to throw back and forth. To keep things interesting there is a tunnel running under the battlefield from one side to the other. Watch out for sneaky players trying to get the jump on you.

Smokes are recommended if you are trying to cross the barren middle of the map.  Be sure to buy your sniper weapons early and often... you will need them!    

Footnote:
=========
Thanks to the JGC Clan for their support.
